name: STRIKE AVIATION TRAINING PTY LTD
about: Strike Aviation Training Pty Ltd, located at Caboolture airfield just north of Brisbane, offers comprehensive pilot training programs tailored to meet your schedule and goals. Our training area includes the picturesque Bribie Island, Glass House Mountains, and Sunshine Coast. Led by CASA-licensed Commercial Pilots with decades of experience, our team is passionate about providing safe, affordable, and fun training on both RAAus and General Aviation (GA) aircraft. We offer initial and advanced training, including part-time and full-time options, to help you achieve your aviation goals. Whether you are starting out or looking to enhance your skills, our dedicated instructors are committed to helping you succeed in the world of aviation. Contact us to start your journey today.
